title: BEAUTIFUL HOUSE STYLE LOFT IN South of Fifth!!
posting_body: ['3 bed / 3.5 Bath luxury loft at Louver House, a newly constructed boutique building on a picturesque tree-lined street designed by Rene Gonzalez.', '2,000 sq ft of exquisitely designed and finished living space with dramatic 11ft ceilings, giant bedrooms w/ensuite baths and telescoping glass doors leading to huge outdoor terraces.', 'Highest quality finishes and fixtures.', 'South of Fifth location in top elementary school district.', 'Walk to the beach and best restaurants, 2 spots, 24 hr security and new rooftop pool.', 'all units are one year lease min!', 'credit score close to 700 or higher required, proof of income 2,5 greater than rent price, first month + last month + security deposit to move in!', 'Dilya Taveras', 'Equity Realty', 'TEXT :', 'show contact info']
